wikipedia_page.main: Edmund James Bradbury (born 10 September 1992) is a British cyclist, who currently rides for British amateur team Pearson Cycles. He previously rode professionally between 2015 and 2019 for the NFTO, JLT–Condor and Memil Pro Cycling teams.
